data.description: Welcome to 3695 Harriett's Bluff! This beautiful marsh front cabin offers breathtaking views and picturesque sunrises and sunsets from its massive front porch. Immerse yourself in the tranquility of nature as you overlook the marsh and enjoy the abundance of wildlife that surrounds you. Launch your kayak right from your front yard and explore the serene waters at your leisure. Step inside and be greeted by the rustic hardwood flooring in the main areas, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The high vaulted ceilings add an extra touch of grandeur, while the two fireplaces provide cozy comfort during the cooler months. You'll love sipping your morning coffee in the spacious sunroom. With three bedrooms and two baths' downstairs, there is ample space for you and all your guest. Upstairs, you'll find a spacious loft with a half bath, perfect for use as an additional bedroom, playroom, or home office. This property also features an RV pad complete with all hookups, providing convenience for those who love to travel and explore. Best of all, there are no HOA's, allowing you the freedom to truly make this property your own. Don't miss out on this unique opportunity to own a marsh front cabin that offers privacy, stunning views, and a chance to connect with nature. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty of 3695 Harriett's Bluff for yourself.
